Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Musical comedy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z98k1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Jan 1976
Sondheim's Japanese story a landmark production in US musical comedy. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.